---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: solutions.html
root: ""
title: Solutions | Green Wing Energy Solutions
description: Technologies we assess and deploy when site conditions suit — refrigeration optimisation, voltage optimisation, FilterPro, EndoTherm, LED lighting and more.
canonical: https://greenwingenergysolutions.com/solutions
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="page-eyebrow">Technologies we assess</p>
    <h1>Solutions</h1>
    <p class="lead">The technologies we assess and deploy when a site's conditions suit them. We stay independent — a solution only appears in your Discovery Assessment Report and Roadmap if the measurement says it belongs there.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section">
  <div class="container prose-wide">
    <p class="text-center lead mb-4">{{ solutionsPage.intro | safe }}</p>
    {% for group in collections.solutionsByCategory %}
    <div class="solution-category">
      <h2>{{ group.category }}</h2>
      {% for item in group.solutions %}
      <article class="solution-block">
        <div class="solution-block-thumb" style="--image-fit: {{ item.data.imageFit or 'cover' }}; --image-position: {{ item.data.imagePosition or 'center center' }}; --image-zoom: {{ item.data.imageZoom or 1 }};">
          <img src="{{ item.data.image | assetPath(root) }}" alt="{{ item.data.imageAlt }}" loading="lazy">
        </div>
        <div class="solution-block-body">
          <h3>{{ item.data.title }}</h3>
          {{ item.templateContent | safe }}
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

{% include "partials/cta-band.njk" %}
